### Create a Booking and Trigger MPESA Payment
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "7d882998-cbe2-4e8a-af8f-2abe3695c3e0",
  "eventId": "24cf38ea-f45a-4ccf-a680-72de404c3f5b",
  "ticketType": "VIP",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Get Bookings by User
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/7d882998-cbe2-4e8a-af8f-2abe3695c3e0
Content-Type: application/json

